    pub values: Option<Vec<String>>,
}

#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Clone, Debug, PartialEq)]
pub enum PostgresqlVolumeSelectorMatchExpressionsOperator {
    DoesNotExist,
    Exists,
    In,
    NotIn,
}
